com.cyc.baseclient.kbtool

Class ObjectToolImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.baseclient.AbstractKbTool
      • com.cyc.baseclient.kbtool.ObjectToolImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ObjectTool

    public class ObjectToolImpl
extends AbstractKbTool
implements ObjectTool
    Tools for creating simple CycObjects, such as constants and lists. To perform complex assertions, use the AssertToolImpl. To lookup facts in the Cyc KB, use the LookupToolImpl.
    Author:
    nwinant
    See Also:
    AssertToolImpl, LookupToolImpl

 ==>
 ((#$Penguin "penguin" #$Bird "bird")
  (#$PittsburghPenguins "the Pittsburgh Penguins" #$IceHockeyTeam "ice hockey team"))
